      {
        "id": "R2X1DZ5WGOGLHP",
        "title": "Easy to install and noticeably gentler water for baby baths",
        "body": "We started using this bath tub filter specifically to help reduce chlorine and make bath time gentler for our baby\u2019s sensitive skin. Installation was very straightforward and took only a couple of minutes\u2014no tools required. It fit securely on our tub spout and didn\u2019t interfere with water pressure, which was a big plus.After a few uses, the water felt noticeably softer, and we saw less dryness on our baby\u2019s skin after baths. It also helped reduce the strong chlorine smell that we normally notice, which made bath time more comfortable overall. The compact design looks clean and unobtrusive, and it doesn\u2019t leak or shift once installed.That said, the filter cartridge will need regular replacement, which is something to factor into the ongoing cost. It also slightly extends the length of the tub spout, so in smaller tubs you may need to adjust how you position your baby during baths.Overall, this filter does exactly what it\u2019s meant to do\u2014provide gentler, cleaner water for baby baths. It\u2019s a solid choice for parents concerned about water quality, especially for babies with sensitive skin, as long as you\u2019re aware of the filter replacement schedule.",
